xylanImaLinkTable.name: xylanImaLinkTable
xylanImaLinkTable.description: A table of IMA link status and configuration information.

xylanImaLinkEntry.name: xylanImaLinkEntry
xylanImaLinkEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about the IMA Link.

xylanImaLinkSlotIndex.name: xylanImaLinkSlotIndex
xylanImaLinkSlotIndex.description: A unique value which identifies this slot.

xylanImaLinkPortIndex.name: xylanImaLinkPortIndex
xylanImaLinkPortIndex.description: A unique value which identifies this port.

xylanImaLinkAdminStatus.name: xylanImaLinkAdminStatus
xylanImaLinkAdminStatus.description: The desired state of this link.

xylanImaLinkIfIndex.name: xylanImaLinkIfIndex
xylanImaLinkIfIndex.description: This indicates the ifIndex of this link.

xylanImaLinkRxIcpCells.name: xylanImaLinkRxIcpCells
xylanImaLinkRxIcpCells.description: This object indicates number of good ICP cells have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkTxIcpCells.name: xylanImaLinkTxIcpCells
xylanImaLinkTxIcpCells.description: This object indicates number of good ICP cells have been transmitted on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxFillerCells.name: xylanImaLinkRxFillerCells
xylanImaLinkRxFillerCells.description: This object indicates number of good filler cells have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkTxFillerCells.name: xylanImaLinkTxFillerCells
xylanImaLinkTxFillerCells.description: This object indicates number of good filler cells have been transmitted on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxAtmLayerCells.name: xylanImaLinkRxAtmLayerCells
xylanImaLinkRxAtmLayerCells.description: This object indicates number of ATM layer cells have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkTxAtmLayerCells.name: xylanImaLinkTxAtmLayerCells
xylanImaLinkTxAtmLayerCells.description: This object indicates number of ATM layer cells have been transmitted on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxBadIcpCells.name: xylanImaLinkRxBadIcpCells
xylanImaLinkRxBadIcpCells.description: This object indicates number of invalid ICP cells have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxBadCrcIcpCells.name: xylanImaLinkRxBadCrcIcpCells
xylanImaLinkRxBadCrcIcpCells.description: This object indicates number of ICP cells with bad CRC-10 have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkCellsInRxBuffer.name: xylanImaLinkCellsInRxBuffer
xylanImaLinkCellsInRxBuffer.description: This object indicates number of cells that are currently in receive buffer on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxBufferFlush.name: xylanImaLinkRxBufferFlush
xylanImaLinkRxBufferFlush.description: This object indicates number of times that receive buffer is flushed on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxBufferOverflow.name: xylanImaLinkRxBufferOverflow
xylanImaLinkRxBufferOverflow.description: This object indicates number of times that receive buffer is overflowed on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxCellDiscarded.name: xylanImaLinkRxCellDiscarded
xylanImaLinkRxCellDiscarded.description: This object indicates number of receive cells that have been discarded on this link.

xylanImaLinkRxStuffEvents.name: xylanImaLinkRxStuffEvents
xylanImaLinkRxStuffEvents.description: This object indicates number of stuff events that have been received on this link.

xylanImaLinkTxStuffEvents.name: xylanImaLinkTxStuffEvents
xylanImaLinkTxStuffEvents.description: This object indicates number of stuff events that have been transmitted on this link.

xylanImaLinkClearStatistics.name: xylanImaLinkClearStatistics
xylanImaLinkClearStatistics.description: Setting this object to clear(2) will clear all statistics of this link to zero's.

xylanImaGroupTable.description: A table of IMA Group status and configuration information.

xylanImaGroupEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about the IMA Group.

xylanImaGroupIndex.name: xylanImaGroupIndex
xylanImaGroupIndex.description: A unique value which identifies this group.

xylanImaGroupDescription.name: xylanImaGroupDescription
xylanImaGroupDescription.description: A string description of this IMA group.

xylanImaGroupAdminStatus.name: xylanImaGroupAdminStatus
xylanImaGroupAdminStatus.description: The desired state of this group.

xylanImaGroupMaxDelaySlot.name: xylanImaGroupMaxDelaySlot
xylanImaGroupMaxDelaySlot.description: A unique value which identifies slot where the link experiences with maximum differential delay within this IMA group.

xylanImaGroupMaxDelayPort.description: A unique value which identifies port where the link experiences with maximum differential delay within this IMA group.

xylanImaGroupAtmLayerSlot.description: A unique value which identifies slot of an ATM layer port where this IMA group is mapped to.

xylanImaGroupAtmLayerPort.description: A unique value which identifies port of an ATM layer port where this IMA group is mapped to.

xylanImaGroupRxAtmLayerCells.description: This object indicates number of ATM layer cells have been received on this group.

xylanImaGroupTxAtmLayerCells.name: xylanImaGroupTxAtmLayerCells
xylanImaGroupTxAtmLayerCells.description: This object indicates number of ATM layer cells have been transmitted on this group.

xylanImaGroupPhyFrameFormat.name: xylanImaGroupPhyFrameFormat
xylanImaGroupPhyFrameFormat.description: This object indicates frame format of all physical links assigned to this group.

xylanImaGroupPhyLoopbackMode.name: xylanImaGroupPhyLoopbackMode
xylanImaGroupPhyLoopbackMode.description: This object indicates loopback configuration of all physical links assigned to this group.

xylanImaGroupPhyLineLength.name: xylanImaGroupPhyLineLength
xylanImaGroupPhyLineLength.description: This object indicates line length of all physical links assigned to this group.

xylanImaGroupPhyTxClkSource.name: xylanImaGroupPhyTxClkSource
xylanImaGroupPhyTxClkSource.description: This object indicates transmit clock source of all physical links assigned to this group.

xylanImaGroupClearStatistics.description: Setting this object to clear(2) will clear all statistics of this group to zero's.

xylanImaGroupPhyUniqueParameter.name: xylanImaGroupPhyUniqueParameter
xylanImaGroupPhyUniqueParameter.description: Whenever a PHY configuration (xylanImaGroupPhyTxClkSource, xylanImaGroupPhyLineLength, xylanImaGroupPhyLoopbackMode, xylanImaGroupPhyFrameFormat) is changed, and this this object is set to yes(1), the new PHY configuration will be applied to all physical ports (T1/E1) in the group.
